<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include("includes/head", { title: 'NOC Application Form' }) %>
    
    <!-- link to stylesheet -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/noc-form.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <%- include("includes/main-header") %> 
      <%- include("includes/nav-header") %>
    </header>

    <main>
      <h3 class="noc-form-heading">
        Student Internship Request form for
        <strong>No Objection Certificate (NOC)</strong>
      </h3>

      <div class="instructions">
        <h4 class="instructions-main-heading">Instructions</h4>

        <h5 class="instructions-sub-heading">
          Do read all instruction carefully mentioned below
        </h5>

        <div>
          <p>
            Dear Students,
            <br />
            All the students, whoever is going for any Internship / Project /
            Training in any Organization, are required to take
            <strong> NO OBJECTION CERTFICATE (NOC) </strong>
            for the same.
            <br />
            <br />
            Do follow the procedure of applying online:-
            <br />
          </p>

          <ol>
            <li>
              Take care of information you are providing in the online form
              which will be printed as it is in the NOC for Internship/Training.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Very Important:</strong>
              Do confirm and write carefully the Name, Designation and Company
              Name & Address in the form to whom you are sending letter/NOC in
              that company/organization. It will be printed as it is. If you do
              mistake in writing spelling of any name, designation or company
              name, it will not be accepted any where. Even a minor mistake of
              Comma (,) will not be considered.
            </li>
            <li>
              You will receive NOC via Email through T&P Cell. It will be an
              automatically generated letter/NOC with date and reference number
              after approval of your Faculty Coordinator/Internship Coordinator
              of your Department and then from T&P Cell. For further proofs you
              can directly take the print of email with all details and live
              link of NOC at our drive if any further proof is required by any
              organization.
            </li>
          </ol>

          <p>
            <strong
              >IMPORTANT NOTE: Do Read each and every instruction given in the
              Online Form and below each field</strong
            >
            <br />
            <br />
            For any query: You may contact to your Faculty Coordinator.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="NOC-form-parent-container">
        <div class="NOC-form-container NOC-form-container-org">
          <h4 class="noc-form-sub-heading">
            Organization details in which you are applying for Internship
          </h4>
  
          <form action="/organization-details.html" method="GET">
            <ul class="input-fields-list">
              <li>
                <label for="org-name">Organization / Company Name</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="org-name"
                  name="org-name"
                  placeholder="Enter Organization / Company Name"
                  required
                />
              </li>
              <li>
                <label for="org-location"
                  >Location / City of Organization / Company</label
                >
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="org-location"
                  name="org-location"
                  placeholder="Enter Location / City of Organization / Company"
                  required
                />
              </li>
              <li>
                <label for="org-person-receiving-noc"
                  >Name of Person receiving NOC in Organization / Company for
                  Internship
                  <br />
                  <span class="extra-instructions"
                    >(If you wanted to send NOC in company by Designation only or
                    you don't know the name, You can leave this BLANK)</span
                  ></label
                >
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="org-person-receiving-noc"
                  name="org-person-receiving-noc"
                  placeholder="Enter Name of Person receiving NOC in Organization / Company for Internship"
                />
              </li>
              <li>
                <label for="org-designation-person-receiving-noc"
                  >Designation of Person receiving NOC in Organization / Company
                  for Internship</label
                >
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="org-designation-person-receiving-noc"
                  name="org-designation-person-receiving-noc"
                  placeholder="Enter Designation of Person receiving NOC in Organization / Company for Internship"
                  required
                />
              </li>
              <li>
                <label for="internship-days">Internship days</label>
                <input
                  type="number"
                  id="internship-days"
                  name="internship-days"
                  placeholder="Enter duration of Internship"
                  required
                />
              </li>
              <li>
                <label for="internship-starting-date"
                  >Internship starting date</label
                >
                <input
                  type="date"
                  name="internship-starting-date"
                  id="internship-starting-date"
                  required
                />
              </li>
              <li>
                <label for="internship-end-date">Internship End date</label>
                <input
                  type="date"
                  id="internship-end-date"
                  name="internship-end-date"
                  required
                />
              </li>
              <li>
                <label for="org-address"
                  >Full Address of organization where you want to go for
                  Internship</label
                >
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="org-address"
                  name="org-address"
                  placeholder="Enter Full Address of organization where you want to go for Internship"
                  required
                />
              </li>
              <li>
                <label for="org-website">Organization website</label>
                <input
                  type="url"
                  id="org-website"
                  name="org-website"
                  placeholder="Enter Organization website"
                  required
                />
              </li>
              <li>
                <label for="applying-through">Applying through</label>
                <select name="applying-through" id="applying-through" required>
                  <option value="" disabled selected hidden>Choose</option>
                  <option value="reference">Employee Reference</option>
                  <option value="internet">Internet / Website</option>
                  <option value="other">Other</option>
                </select>
              </li>
              <li>
                <label for="internship-offer-letter"
                  >Internship Offer Letter or Approval mail from Organization
                  <span class="extra-instructions">(If any)</span></label
                >
                <input
                  type="file"
                  name="internship-offer-letter"
                  id="internship-offer-letter"
                />
              </li>
              <li>
                <label for="self-declaration">Self Declaration</label>
                <div id="self-declaration-container">
                  <input
                    type="checkbox"
                    id="self-declaration"
                    name="self-declaration"
                    required
                  />
                  <label for="self-declaration"
                    >I hereby declare that the information given in this
                    application is true and correct to the best of my knowledge
                    and belief. In case any information given in this application
                    proves to be false or incorrect, I shall be responsible for
                    the consequences.</label
                  >
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
  
            <div class="button-container">
              <button type="reset" class="btn-alt">Clear Form</button>
              <button type="submit" class="btn">Submit</button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <%- include("includes/footer") %>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
